To compile:
$ g++ -std=c++11 -stdlib=libc++ -c *.cpp

To link on MacOS:
$  g++ -framework OpenGL -framework GLUT *.o -o maze

To link on Linux (not tested):
$  g++ -lGL -lGLU -lglut *.o -o maze

To link on other OSes see:
https://web.eecs.umich.edu/~sugih/courses/eecs487/glut-howto/

To run:
$ ./maze <optional_maze_file>




